    "body": "That's matplotlib, IPython does not set colors.\n\nTo set matplotlib's color cycle, set this in your matplotlibrc:\n\n```\naxes.color_cycle = color1, color2, etc.\n```\n\nor, at runtime:\n\n```\nimport matplotlib\nmatplotlib.rc('axes', color_cycle=['r', 'g', 'b', '#004060'])\n```\n\netc.\n"
